Application Requirement
-----------------------
At least PHP 5.x


Application environment configuration
-------------------------------------
config/config.php - Set the absolute path of this project. [DO NOT COMMIT THIS FILE]
config/databases.yml - Config the username/password to the database. [DO NOT COMMIT THIS FILE]
config/propel.ini - Config the absolution location of the propel.output.dir. [DO NOT COMMIT THIS FILE]


Application Database Setup
--------------------------
To create the database, model file. Command line version of php work better. Execute commands under the 
root directory of the project.

  php symfony propel-build-all
  php symfony propel-load-data backend
  
To load video for testing purpose, run
  php batch/loadTestVideo.php
  

Setup Apache for the Application
--------------------------------
mod_rewrite must be enabled. You must point apache to web directory.
Example,

<Directory "C:/work/phpdirector/branches/buildWithSymfony/web">
    AllowOverride All
    Options Indexes FollowSymLinks 
    Order allow,deny
    Allow from all
</Directory>


Unit & Functional Test Case
---------------------------
All Test Case are store under test directory. To run these test case, run

  php symfony test-all